            <div type="transcript" id="J1506">
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Summer is shorter than any one --</l>
                    <l>Life is shorter than Summer --</l>
                    <l>Seventy Years is spent as quick</l>
                    <l>As an Only Dollar --</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Sorrow -- now -- is polite -- and stays --</l>
                    <l>See how well we spurn him --</l>
                    <l>Equally to abhor Delight --</l>
                    <l>Equally retain him --</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>5. Sorrow] Aroma --</l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
